### Dynamic DB Connect
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dbType": "POSTGRES",
  "host": "localhost",
  "port": 5432,
  "database": "ssm_test",
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "secret"
}

### Dynamic DB Close
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT"
}

### Dynamic Products - 查詢所有商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "limit": 50
}

### Dynamic Products - 依 SKU 查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "sku": "EL-USB-C-01"
}

### Dynamic Products - 依商品名稱模糊查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "productName": "USB"
}

### Dynamic Products - 依類別查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "categoryId": 1
}

### Dynamic Products - 查詢啟用商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "isActive": true
}

### Dynamic Products - 價格範圍查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "UUID_FROM_CONNECT",
  "minListPrice": 500,
  "maxListPrice": 1500,
  "isActive": true,
  "limit": 20
}
